Copy this to `vault-system/product-impact/scripts/publish_articles.py`
and customise the vault-specific parts marked TODO.

Usage:
  python3 publish_articles.py drafts/claude-46-platform-shift.md
  python3 publish_articles.py drafts/*.md                          # batch
  python3 publish_articles.py --dry-run drafts/article.md          # validate + image gen, no publish

Flow:
  1. Parse vault markdown (your parser) → article dict
  2. validate_article.py — block publish if required fields are missing
  3. generate_hero_image.py — create + upload hero image if frontmatter is null
  4. Link entities (from [[wiki links]] in the body → article_entities rows)
  5. supabase.table("articles").upsert(...)
  6. Move draft → published/YYYY/MM/ for audit trail
  7. dispatch_rebuild.py — trigger CF Pages rebuild (once at end of batch)

Env vars required:
  ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, REPLICATE_API_TOKEN, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY,
  PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL, PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, GITHUB_TOKEN
"""

from __future__ import annotations

import argparse
import json
